lead_paragraph: Manager Eddie Howe is focussed on ensuring young players coming through the ranks at Bournemouth can fulfil their potential and even go on to forge international careers.

headline.print_headline: Howe Wants Young Cherries to Ripen Into Pick of the Bunch
